      <title>绘制全球经济图：欧洲央行维持利率稳定，而美国失业率上升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-09/world-economy-latest-ecb-holds-rates-steady-while-us-unemployment-rate-rises</link>
